aim_sag_fastaim
==================
Aim - Combat/Skill
SAG - Maptype relevant for my team so irrelevant for you guys.
fastaim - Mapseries of "quick action aim maps" information as to the size of the map.

The map is symmetric and has 40 spawns in total. You have buyzones and nothing really amazing or fancy. Lighting is rendered to use HDR.
